<h1 class="part-title">Update prisoner information</h1>
<div class="govuk-inset-text">
  Senior Probation Officer / Head of Offender Management Unit (SPO/HoOMU) / Case admin task
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-column">
  <div class="govuk-body">

    <div class="govuk-warning-text">
      <span class="govuk-warning-text__icon" aria-hidden="true">!</span>
      <strong class="govuk-warning-text__text">
        <span class="govuk-warning-text__assistive">Warning</span>
        Please note: This task can’t be started until <%=link_to "Task 3: Set up POMs in NOMIS","help_step3" %> has been completed
      </strong>
    </div>


    <p>You will need to update information about some prisoners in the allocations
      service before you can start allocating POMs. This involves getting information
      from NDelius and recording:
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Whether the service provider is NPS or CRC</li>
      <li>The prisoner’s tier</li>
      <li>Whether the prisoner has a Welsh address (this is because Wales is piloting the new OMiC policy before it is rolled out across England)</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Sign in to <%= link_to("https://moic.service.justice.gov.uk", "https://moic.service.justice.gov.uk") %> and follow these steps:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>go to ‘update case information’</li>
      <li>Select ‘edit’ by the name of the prisoner whose information needs updating</li>
      <li>Answer the questions and ‘Save’</li>
    </ul>

    <div>
      <ul class="pagination-next">
        <li class="gem-c-pagination__item gem-c-pagination__item--next">
          <a href=<%= help_step6_path %> class="gem-c-pagination__link" rel="next">
          <span class="gem-c-pagination__link-title">
            <svg class="gem-c-pagination__link-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="13" width="17" viewBox="0 0 17 13">
              <path fill="currentColor" d="m10.107-0.0078125-1.4136 1.414 4.2926 4.293h-12.986v2h12.896l-4.1855 3.9766 1.377 1.4492 6.7441-6.4062-6.7246-6.7266z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="gem-c-pagination__link-text">
              Next
            </span>
          </span>
            <span class="gem-c-pagination__link-divider visually-hidden">:</span>
            <span class="gem-c-pagination__link-label">Start making allocations</span>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
